# KSV014: readOnlyRootFilesystem cannot be enabled for the LSIO Home Assistant image.
# The s6-overlay init system writes to the root filesystem during container startup
# (service definitions, runtime state). Setting readOnlyRootFilesystem: true breaks the init.
# Mitigated by: seccompProfile RuntimeDefault, PUID 1000 (HA process non-root), capabilities drop ALL.
KSV014
